  "title": "Full Time Service Crew",
  "description": "<p>- Handle daily operations activities (hands-on) such as Cashiering, Kitchen duties, and Tea making<br />- Involve in closing of shop (only applicable for night shift staff)<br />- Attend to walk-in customers promptly<br />- Maintain cleanliness and tidiness in work areas<br />- Assist in stock taking / recording<br />- Answer incoming calls and handle delivery orders<br /></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p>- No experience required as on-the-job training will be provided<br />- Pleasant disposition and well-groomed<br />- Cooperative and helpful with other team members<br />- Excellent and positive service attitude<br />- Able to work shifts, weekends, eve of public holidays and public holidays on <strong>5.5 days per week</strong>, on <strong>rotating shifts</strong><br />- Minimum 6 months commitment<br />- Independent and able to multi-task<br />- Able to commence work in short notice will be an added advantage<br />- Only Singaporean/PR may apply<br /><br /><strong>Benefits:</strong></p><ol><li>Career advancement</li><li><strong>7 off days per month</strong></li><li>Overtime pay</li><li>Medical subsidies</li><li>Dental benefits</li><li>TCM benefits</li><li>Staff drink</li><li>Other allowances*</li></ol><p>* Terms and Conditions apply.<br /><br />We regret that only shortlisted candidate would be contacted.</p>",
