    "description": "<p>KOI CAFÉ GROUP PTE. LTD., established in 2007, the overseas headquarters of Taiwan YA-LAN CO. LTD. The vision of the organization is to provide high quality products with emphasis on customized beverages for meeting the satisfaction of each individual customer. KOI CAFÉ upholds the spirit of customer-first and providing the original taste of Taiwan Bubble Tea to different parts of the world. On 1st September 2016, KOI CAFÉ GROUP (S) PTE. LTD. has acquired new name, KOI THÉ&nbsp;SINGAPORE PTE. LTD. THÉ&nbsp;means “TEA” in French, its pronunciation also sounds like Taiwanese “TÉ”. KOI THÉ has successfully expanded to 83&nbsp;outlets in Singapore, and in 12 other countries over the world.</p>",
